I also feel that Spooky's Jump Scare Mansion's early presentation fits well with the cute channel image. Cute shark likes horror game, plays cute game that turn into horror.

You can watch an old trailer here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XGhqaCHt2Jw the game has seen a lot of updates since then.
 Its getting another expansion on October 1st as well.

author: @BlackStar300

text:
¬†@BlackStar300¬† ¬†@BlackStar300¬† Welcome to the community. It is not a dedicated SC stream , it's a dedicated SC THANKING stream . It usually comes if they have too many SC to thank the day before and they will have a dedicated session to thank everyone who donated previously.


Even on a dedicated SC THANKING stream , there's no guarantee they won't miss your donation. So it's best to donate with the intention of supporting the girls and not donate because of that 1 second of shout out .
author: @albee8182

text: ¬†@albee8182¬†  Ty for the welcom! Definitely new experience, but wow I can't help the Shark! So my SC will be read on a stream dedicated to SC thanking stream? Just not sure how far back they go depending on when they do their next stream lol. Like if its a few streams later she does one IDK if they go from newest to oldest or oldest to newest. :x
author: @BlackStar300

text: ¬†@BlackStar300¬† Yup that's exactly my point . They might begin thanking at the point where you have already donated and missed it . So if you like to donate , I think it would be better to donate without any expectations , treat the name shout-out as a bonus =)
author: @albee8182

text: ¬†@albee8182¬† oh boy this is gonna be tough . I might have to do smaller donos. I did a $10 and then a $5 today. I'm not rich. I definitely will get the membership so supporting isn't an issue by any means, just want a S/O!
